messages.messageBody:
For right now, fanfiction that is archived in the Files section of
this site will be how it gets loaded onto the SHQ website. That's
subject to change as we build things and organize, but for right now,
that's the routine. Keep in mind that Barb is working fast & furious
and it may take some time for things to even "be" routine. She's
dealing with LOTS of information over on miburo & SHQ.

So get writing, Andy (or is it Andie?)!! :-)
phil
